snippet.title: Grand Fantasia Official Trailer [2012]
snippet.description:
Embark on a journey full of wonder and intrigue in Grand Fantasia. Create a hero and a faithful Sprite companion to accompany you on your adventures. http://grandfantasia.aeriagames.com/playnow

Congratulations to the winners of our Grand Fantasia Trailer contest -- Egni, Kyle015 and TwistingSparks! You can see their awesome footage here. 

A big thank you to everyone who submitted gameplay footage! Check out prize details in the the GF forums: http://www.aeriagames.com/forums/en/viewtopic.php?t=1613203
